name: Terminus
description: Welcome to Terminus, the meme cryptocurrency that's out of this world! Inspired by humanity's relentless drive to explore the cosmos, Terminus is your ticket to the final frontier of crypto. Our logo, a rocket triumphantly perched on the red sands of Mars, symbolizes our mission to reach new heights in the meme economy.
